p: The title compound was obtained in 51% yield from compound 33 following the general procedure for Suzuki arylation: 1H NMR (300 MHz, CDCl 3) δ 3.91 (s, 3H), 4.69 (s, 2H), 6.67 (d, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.19 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 1H), 7.43 (t, J = 8.1 Hz, 1H), 7.52 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 2H), 7.83 (m, 1H), 8.02 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 2H), 8.39 (s, 1H), 9.00 (d, J = 2.4 Hz, 1H).
